sec.p:
Figure 1 shows a simplified diagram of such a system. The piezoelectric harvester (PEH) is excited with acceleration from the environment which is converted into current due to the piezoelectric effect. The PEH can be modeled as a current source in parallel with a parasitic capacitance CP\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
