As can be seen, the regulated voltage level differs between the converters. This is due to different offset voltages of the comparators used in the regulation loop. Looking at the output voltage the converters maintain an output voltage of 1.8 V ±10%\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
